  <prompt>
    Delete the divergent local `CalendarSection.tsx` in `src/solutions/CalendarSidePane/` and import the
    component from `@spaarke/events-components` (the same component used by SpaarkeAi's embedded Calendar
    widget). Verify CalendarSidePane on record forms looks + behaves IDENTICALLY to SpaarkeAi's embedded
    Calendar version. Dark-mode parity test included (ADR-021).
  </prompt>

  <role>
    React/Fluent UI v9 developer familiar with the dual-use Pattern D (Calendar widget — R3 task 115,
    canonical reference per `SPAARKEAI-COMPONENTIZATION-AUDIT.md` §2A). Bias toward exact parity over
    cleanups: this is a unification, not a rewrite.
  </role>

  <goal>
    (a) `src/solutions/CalendarSidePane/src/components/CalendarSection.tsx` (local copy) deleted; (b)
    `src/solutions/CalendarSidePane/src/App.tsx` (or wherever it's consumed) imports `CalendarSection`
    from `@spaarke/events-components` instead; (c) CalendarSidePane on record forms is visually +
    behaviorally identical to SpaarkeAi's embedded Calendar widget (FR-09 acceptance); (d) dark-mode
    parity verified (ADR-021); (e) deploy CalendarSidePane web resource and verify post-deploy.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec FR-09 (B-6) + plan §4 Phase 5: `SPAARKEAI-COMPONENTIZATION-AUDIT.md` flagged the divergent
      local copy. CalendarSidePane and SpaarkeAi's embedded Calendar widget should be the SAME COMPONENT
      — they diverged because `@spaarke/events-components` was created after CalendarSidePane shipped
      (the shared lib emerged from R10 hoist work). The hoist canonical form (`CalendarSection` in
      `Spaarke.Events.Components/src/components/CalendarSection/CalendarSection.tsx`) is the post-hoist
      version. The CalendarSidePane local copy is the pre-hoist version.

      Risk: a subtle divergence (different prop, different default, different className) could change
      record-form rendering. Mitigation: pre-change visual snapshot of CalendarSidePane in record-form
      context; post-change comparison; dark-mode verified.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/solutions/CalendarSidePane/src/components/CalendarSection.tsx (delete)</file>
      <file>src/solutions/CalendarSidePane/src/App.tsx (import update)</file>
      <file>src/client/shared/Spaarke.Events.Components/src/components/CalendarSection/CalendarSection.tsx (canonical)</file>
